snippet.title: [SM64 Major Hack] Ztar Attack Rebooted Release Video
snippet.description:
Remade version of original Ztar Attack 1 by TheGael95 is finally here! Featuring 170 Ztars, reworked smaller levels and new gimmicks. Hack is beginner friendly yet it gets more challenging closer to end.

Good Luck and have fun!

Download Links:
Z64: https://mega.nz/#!qfJHEITR!th8CzwgQ1QXA-apolJbfo7wOIRBLIDrSsXHqCiOh_xQ
BPS Patch: https://mega.nz/#!KCIRGSCQ!nQrRUP80JqtVdfVPCwuvxKPOLkFLjgHiioWNeM0T4q0
WiiVC WAD: https://mega.nz/#!vXomFYhS!VUiikyqV6YfhAAyQA1tYswLF3Ly49OjQhfd20d5QVvw

Recommended emulator is PJ64 1.6 https://mega.nz/#!Lb5FTCoT!hZCr5G5UHxno-XufXDnT9bsghN_aM33m7fq57y4ewq4
GLideN64 video plugin optimized for PJ64 1.6 http://www.mediafire.com/file/k9ad2bdodde327u/GLideN64-sm64hacks.zip/file
Game ASM Sources https://github.com/aglab2/sm64asm/tree/master/za1-rebooted

If any glitch happens, please send savestate!

Other released hacks: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL-jWm9AsqM7JbR2ZblWh7uHynikAuBKcq
